48
00:02:58,805 --> 00:02:59,973
Yeah.

49
00:03:06,020 --> 00:03:08,106
Great. One sec.

50
00:03:23,371 --> 00:03:24,706
This okay with you?

51
00:03:26,082 --> 00:03:27,250
Of course.

52
00:03:28,251 --> 00:03:31,337
Yeah. I just mean...

53
00:03:32,589 --> 00:03:36,134
this might not be what you dreamed of
