54
00:03:37,677 --> 00:03:41,848
Jimmy, it's not about that.
This is just, you know...

55
00:03:43,391 --> 00:03:44,726
everything we talked about.

56
00:03:44,809 --> 00:03:46,394
Right. Right. I know.

57
00:03:47,395 --> 00:03:49,063
Just making sure.

58
00:03:50,607 --> 00:03:53,484
