And you have your witnesses.

67
00:04:50,917 --> 00:04:52,669
Okay, then.

68
00:04:52,752 --> 00:04:54,295
Here we go.

69
00:04:56,297 --> 00:04:59,425
Here we go.

70
00:05:04,138 --> 00:05:08,184
Do you, James Morgan McGill,
